Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:12.25,JoJo-Location,meh,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.53,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a doner kebab place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we stop and get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Doner kebabs are the\N hamburgers of the Middle East!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:31.17,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,A slab of meat is placed on a spit, \Nand its surface roasts as it turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.92,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,They then shave off the cooked meat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and eat it on bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It is quite a delicious dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. I'd like five of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.51,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Five will cost you a thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.99,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the Middle East, the logic of Japan and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.68,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,the West doesn't apply at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, prices are very unspecific.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.95,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Foreigners who come here for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.44,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,with no understanding of the art of haggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,have no idea what things cost\N and are easily exploited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,But in this world, such exploitation \Nis not seen as a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.91,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was tricked into \Nbuying is seen as an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:09.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,I will now explain how to buy things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.96,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:17.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, for instance, \Nact like you see through the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:23.12,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me, now! That's far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.51,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and laugh out loud. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.97,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,How much would you buy them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,...they will ask the customer\N how much they're willing to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Make it 250 yen for five!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,In return, the customer names a price so low,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd feel a bit guilty even saying it. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take the attitude, \N"Seriously? Have you no sense?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and act as though you're mocking them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:51.42,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,If I sold them for that much, \Nmy whole family would starve to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:54.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Then they will gesture as if\N their head were being cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.86,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,But you mustn't give up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:01.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll just buy them somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.59,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Act like you're leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:06.69,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, friend! I'm very kind to foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.23,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sell you five for 700 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.68,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and they'll say that to try and stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.83,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Make it 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.71,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Let the haggling begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.05,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,600!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,350!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.28,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,550!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,400!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.35,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,450!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.61,JoJo-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,425!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.37,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I got them for less \Nthan half his original price!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:31.18,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! I made out like a bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.00,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,And just as you think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.27,JoJo-internal/narrator,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I usually sell five for 150 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.46,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That old lady's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.14,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:04.61,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... I haven't said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:09.49,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you here before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.09,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that I, Enyaba,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:15.58,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,would actually tell them\N the secret of Lord DIO's Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:28.18,JoJo-Menacing,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(418,1)}Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are these tentacles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.48,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:48.54,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you come to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:54.49,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It means that Lord DIO truly trusts no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:58.97,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I will be making sure you never speak again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.25,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,And as for you four there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.43,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I will be taking your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:10.97,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:14.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.21,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.90,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Dan of Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.01,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand suggests The Lovers card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:27.36,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I will see to it that you all\N meet the same fate as Enyaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.89,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.12,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That old lady was one of you, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.02,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-Lies... Lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.47,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:45.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO would never do this to me....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.45,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The thing coming out of the\N old lady's body is not a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.05,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,They're real! They're real, moving tentacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:58.23,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,He would never do something like this to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.65,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,He would never plant a flesh bud...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.15,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Flesh bud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:10.32,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO is my reason to live...\NWe trust each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.53,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.02,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,They melted from the rays of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.17,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The flesh bud! It's DIO's own cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.77,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely! I'm impressed you \Nwere able to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.03,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,That is what the flesh bud, \Nmade from Lord DIO's cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.55,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,looks like when it's grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:38.52,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I just grew it inside of Enyaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.68,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Enyaba, I hear that you were the one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who told Lord DIO about the Stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.95,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no way that Lord DIO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:49.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,would ever trust a little\N old woman like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.28,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you hadn't realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what the true \Nidentity of DIO's Stand is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.02,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You placed your hope and trust in DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:10.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And now you know he's not \Nthe man you thought he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:14.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I have to defeat DIO! Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:21.22,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Tell me about DIO's Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:28.02,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Lord... DIO...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.55,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,He believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.71,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.27,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.86,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,How sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:02.16,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,How truly sad that old woman was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.32,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that she trusted him so deeply
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.81,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,shows how powerful Lord DIO's evil charm truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.87,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Since Enyaba was connected with my sister's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.70,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty conflicted about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.94,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be four against one,\N but we won't hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.30,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.79,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.75,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.32,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to act cool at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.81,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you won't attack us, we're going to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.28,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.08,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of you will
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:54.07,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,be able to even lay a\N finger upon me, Dan of Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.07,JoJo-Smash,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.61,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.09,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened, Mr. Joestar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:04.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,He flew back just like that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:09.82,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! I was still in the \Nmiddle of my explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.92,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You were very close to killing \Nyour own grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.80,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:25.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I appeared \Nbefore you just to kill Enyaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.30,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you had the Stand\N of the Lovers' card, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:34.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:39.95,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,The battle has already begun, Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.83,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:47.45,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you look,\N you won't be able to find my Stand easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.12,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:55.09,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a tip,\N so hit my leg with your broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.47,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:03.97,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.73,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Mr. Joestar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.73,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, \Nbut there's tremendous pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:18.78,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't figured it out, Joseph Joestar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.37,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand goes inside the bodies of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:28.37,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,The moment Enyaba died,\Nit entered your brain through your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.69,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.61,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, the Stand and \Nmyself are one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.93,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,If my Stand gets hurt, so do I, and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.81,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,If you so much as scratch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.77,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,my Stand, which is within your brain, \Nwill react to my pain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.56,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in that same moment by going berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.82,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It will inflict pain several times greater \Nto the same part of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.94,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:04.95,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You will not be able to \Nlay a single finger on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:11.26,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, The Lovers has\N taken Lord DIO's flesh bud into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.58,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It's growing within your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.42,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Enyaba, it will eat you \Nfrom the inside and you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.52,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,When did I say you could strike me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.60,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:37.54,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, my Stand, \NThe Lovers, is very weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.01,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't powerful enough to\N move even a single strand of hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.97,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the world's weakest Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.11,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.66,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need power to kill humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.75,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.09,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(712,1)}The Lovers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.09,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(878,1)}Dan of Steel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:06.26,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to be in a car accident, \Nhit by a baseball,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:10.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or even to trip and fall, Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:15.98,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Your body would suffer far \Ngreater damage than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.44,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can even feel real pain \Nin my artificial left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.71,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,And in ten minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:28.44,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,your brain will be eaten through, \Nand you will die like Enyaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.76,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, calm down! Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:39.88,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm going to kill him so quickly,\N he won't have a moment to feel pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:51.22,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Without a moment to feel pain, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.43,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.19,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see you try it, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.68,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.24,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you planning to destroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.94,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! My face? My throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:09.07,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's wrong? Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.51,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just see what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.20,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,How about busting a hole through my chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.18,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Or how about you give \Nup on using your Stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.62,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and crack my head open with a rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.97,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll even get the rock for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.71,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one big enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.84,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.32,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I say I'm going to do something, I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.40,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything rash, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.12,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You've already seen his powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill your own grandfather?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.73,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's the type that might actually do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.91,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't taking me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:58.93,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.08,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.75,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:12.44,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,After the geezer Joestar dies, next it'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.40,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.44,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,...your brain that I send The Lovers into and kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:21.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.09,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandson is being beaten up to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.04,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely caught up in his pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.10,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,His Stand is inside my brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:40.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,When I was younger, there was a time when \Npoison was placed into my heart, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.24,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I must do something... I must do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.49,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:58.68,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! Keep him away from Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.23,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get as far\N away from him as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.72,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:09.12,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think that if you move far enough away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my Stand's power will disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:16.52,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,But one's weakness can also be one's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:21.85,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand, The Lovers, may be weak, \Nbut once it is within a body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:25.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can control it from a distance \Nfar greater than any other Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even hundreds of kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:33.55,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jotaro! I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.10,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking away so calmly for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.18,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.81,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you're starting to lose your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:48.57,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to follow me until Joseph dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.53,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Dan, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:54.07,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely make you pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.42,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,If that's why you're following me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I should borrow a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.12,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:16.75,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I see that your watch, audaciously \Nenough, is a TAG Heuer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.22,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be borrowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:26.70,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:31.28,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's an electronics store! \NMr. Joestar, they have TVs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:37.36,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff, did you think \Nwe were just running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.62,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight the \NStand that's inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.62,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:46.51,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,We only have a few minutes.\N You'll be assisting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.37,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.84,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hermit Purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.10,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.90,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:05.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How can it be that I had to \Nsee inside my own brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:09.76,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can see now that \Nthere's a really tiny Stand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.94,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,inside of you, Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:15.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But how do you plan on defeating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:19.78,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Your Stand and mine will enter \NMr. Joestar's body, and defeat it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.67,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.55,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stands are images made of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.38,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be able to shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.50,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take it easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.46,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to lose.\N We're going in, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.24,JoJo-main,hiero,0000,0000,0000,,Hierophant Green!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.97,JoJo-main,silver,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.07,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.10,JoJo-main,gren,0000,0000,0000,,Get smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.73,JoJo-main,green,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be entering a blood vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.73,JoJo-main,silver,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.23,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,A drainage ditch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.99,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I could jump across this ditch,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:05.76,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,but if I were to trip and twist my \Nankle, it could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.50,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a pain to go all the way \Nto that bridge over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.55,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.57,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down across this ditch \Nand make yourself into a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk over it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:21.17,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not going to be my bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.76,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:29.23,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I said, make yourself into a bridge!\N You ridiculous bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.73,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:33.48,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,M-My leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.08,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's going numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is Jotaro doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.00,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.30,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.47,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:27.89,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,You're a rather sturdy bridge, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.60,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you? Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.97,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.82,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.23,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.34,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.16,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy's Stand, The Lovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:50.02,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is in the brain stem, the point \Nwhere the nervous system begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:53.98,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff and I will enter the \Nvein from inside your ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.36,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,then swim through the blood \Nvessels toward the brain stem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff, open a hole in the \Nwall of the blood vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hold on a second! \NYou're using your Stands, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.86,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just slip through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.36,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,At this size, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood vessel's wall is too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:15.35,JoJo-main,kkayo,0000,0000,0000,,The hole will be microscopic,\N so there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:20.13,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting through a blood \Nvessel or nerve right now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,would take several minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:25.01,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, our Stands would have \Nalready cut down the enemy Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.04,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Though we may have already started...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.44,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping our Stands this\N small is really exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:36.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It requires a lot of Stand power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:38.81,JoJo-main,silver,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:48.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God! I-I don't feel so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:37.06,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:37.82,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,My back itches...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:40.35,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a really good mood right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.64,JoJo-main,dan,0000,0000,0000,,How about I have you lick it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:45.61,JoJo-main,thing,0000,0000,0000,,The one who knows himself best will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.10,JoJo-main,thing,0000,0000,0000,,Everything begins when
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:50.07,JoJo-main,thing,0000,0000,0000,,you acknowledge your own weakness!
